## Usage 
```bash
$ lolcat-cc -h
lolcat-cc is a cross-platform c++ implementation of lolcat, 
which writes output to the terminal with rainbow colours
=> usage:
 command | lolcat-cc (options)
 lolcat-cc (options) file
=> options:
      -f: format
  -g=[d]: set gradient
     -ln: line numbers
     -ps: powershell colours
 -tw=[i]: set tab width
      -v: print version
  -w=[i]: set width
...
